WEBVTT

00:06.965 --> 00:09.758
<i>Previously
on AMC's "The Son"...</i>

00:09.802 --> 00:11.427
I'd rather die
than be a slave.

00:11.470 --> 00:13.178
Who blew up my rig?!

00:13.222 --> 00:15.262
Let the people know in your
heart you're a Comanche.

00:16.475 --> 00:18.350
We start killing folks
like the old days,

00:18.394 --> 00:19.434
it's gonna become a habit.

00:20.563 --> 00:22.396
This club is
my hiding place.

00:23.858 --> 00:25.899
I'm not running off
with a married man.

00:25.943 --> 00:27.192
Tar.

00:27.236 --> 00:28.652
And it's a mile
on the wrong side

00:28.696 --> 00:30.070
of my neighbor's fence.

00:30.114 --> 00:31.834
Pedro García
ain't gonna go without a fight.

00:31.866 --> 00:33.198
Get that dynamite ready.

00:34.952 --> 00:36.243
Come on.

